#

Classic Baked Potatoes with Sour Cream and Chives

70 min
$8
280 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodEasySide Dish

Description

Fluffy baked potatoes topped with creamy sour cream and fresh chives for a simple yet satisfying dish.

Ingredients

  • russet potatoes: 4 large
  • sour cream: 1 cup
  • chives: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
